    "An overview of the taxonomy and the coverage of the underlying concepts across the categories is presented in Fig. 5.",
    "As mentioned previously, we obtained multiple concepts for each category.",
    "Some concepts were common across some categories whereas some were unique.",
    "For example, 'AI ethics & principles' is a concept that emerged for each of the five categories, depicted by a full circle around the five categories.",
    "The 'teams-related' concept emerged for three categories, namely, practitioner awareness, practitioner need, and practitioner approach, depicted by a crescent that covers these three categories on the top left."
